@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zumzcw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.12 / tmp + 0.14)) - (v0 - 0.17))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.39 * tmp + 0.77)) / wp.exp(0.81))
    v1 = 0.66
    v0 = (v2 - wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.05)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v1) * (0.39 / 0.04))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v1) - (tmp / (v0 + 0.84 * v2 + 0.13)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
